SECRET
No. 75/CF/52
GOVERNMENT OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
New Delhi, the 17th September, 1957.
The undersigned is directed to inform Members
of the Council of Ministers that the Prime Minister,
will look after the Ministry of Finance during the
absence of Shri T.T. Krishnamachari, who is going abroad
today.
****
Rameshchand
KOHLI
300 copies.
(Ramesh Chandra)
for Secretary to the Cabinet.

Copy forwarded to the Deputy Chairman, Planning
Commission, for information.
Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President/the Special Assistant
to the Prime Minister/the Principal Private Secretary to the
Prime Minister, for information.
Nameshchandr
